commit message: Use a module to provide the presenter so it can be easily mocked in the next step.
Modified tests so the test components pull the necessary dependency from the component.
Use apt instead of kapt for annotation processing.

Added a book adding / removing test for the BookShelfFragment.

Also subclassed App in testing so the dependencies can be mocked easily.
Modified the test so books will be removed at the same time.
Test activity restart in combination with book adding.
Enable ACRA in debug mode and forward it to timber.
Plant a dummy log tree that will later log to disc
Buffer removed books on back pressure as there can be a lot in a really short time.
